<h1>Instructions</h1>

<p>First thing you want to do is register. In order to register you need to provide all of the requested information.
   The e-mail you enter only needs to match an e-mail format (since there is no interaction with it).</p>

<h2>Main Page</h2>
<p>This is where you choose a quiz to solve simply by clicking "solve" button at the end of each table row.
   When solving question, simply choose the desired answer from those given in drop-down list and pressing "Next" button.
   When the last question is answered you are redirected back to Main Page.</p>
<p style="color: red; font-weight: bold">Warning: if you leave the quiz by missclicking or connection error you WILL NOT be able to finish it
    and will be given ONLY the points you acquired up until that point.</p>

<h2>Profile</h2>
<p>Here you can check out your statistics so far as well as edit your user name and photo. In the table below you can check how you performed in each
   individual quiz. By pressing the "More" button you can check which questions you answered correctly and see correct answers of those you didn't.</p>

<h2>Edit login info</h2>
<p>A place to change your login information.</p>

<h2>Rankings</h2>
<p>List of all players and their stats, sorted based on number of points. For a different order, click on the column name (once for descending, once more for ascending).
   If you are currently logged your stats will be marked with grey background.</p>

